 call on Jan 23, 2026.\nThe call aimed to provide insights into recent financial performance for investors.","url":"https://www.marketscreener.com/news/transcript-tanla-platforms-limited-q3-2026-earnings-call-jan-23-2026-ce7e5bdad88cf427","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T00:00:00","source":"MarketScreener"},{"id":"802176369521272576","title":"Tanla Platforms' Q3 net profit rose 10.8% to ₹131.3 Cr, revenue up 12.1% to ₹1,121 Cr.\nEBITDA grew 16.9% to ₹190.5 Cr, with margins improving to 17% from 16.3% YoY.","summary":"Tanla Platforms' Q3 net profit rose 10.8% to ₹131.3 Cr, revenue up 12.1% to ₹1,121 Cr.\nEBITDA grew 16.9% to ₹190.5 Cr, with margins improving to 17% from 16.3% YoY.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=802176369521272636","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-22T19:32:30","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"260115132190749","title":"Tanla Platforms' EPS grew 49% annually over five years, but its share price fell 38%. Revenue increased 12% annually.\nDespite a 5-year TSR of 34%, shareholders lost 24% in the past year, underperforming the market's 7.6% gain.","summary":"Tanla Platforms' EPS grew 49% annually over five years, but its share price fell 38%. Revenue increased 12% annually.\nDespite a 5-year TSR of 34%, shareholders lost 24% in the past year, underperforming the market's 7.6% gain.","url":"https://simplywall.st/stocks/in/software/nse-tanla/tanla-platforms-shares/news/the-five-year-underlying-earnings-growth-at-tanla-platforms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-15T06:34:03","source":"Simply Wall Street"},{"id":"438698","title":"Tanla Platforms schedules a board meeting on Jan 22, 2026, to approve Q3 and 9-month FY25 unaudited results.\nAn earnings call discussing these results is set for Jan 23, 2026, at 3:30 PM IST.","summary":"Tanla Platforms schedules a board meeting on Jan 22, 2026, to approve Q3 and 9-month FY25 unaudited results.\nAn earnings call discussing these results is set for Jan 23, 2026, at 3:30 PM IST.","url":"https://www.bs